        <table class="compare-table">
          <tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What it does</th><th>Real-life example</th></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Reducing</strong></td><td>Collapse many elements into one value</td><td>Sum all prices to get a total</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Mapping</strong></td><td>Transform each element, producing a new list of the same length</td><td>Capitalize every name in a list</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Filtering</strong></td><td>Keep only elements that meet a condition</td><td>Select only the passing grades from a score list</td></tr>
